    ns1:itemIndex 42 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "4.6. Laboratory V: Mechanical characterization of engineering materials"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000604/2025-26/syllabus/43> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 43 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "4.6.1. The students will perform tensile tests on different materials, evaluating the effect of deformation and temperature on the obtained results. Hardness and fracture toughness will also be evaluated by means of indentation. Sin subniveles"@es .

